{"tid":1031412,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"浸大好波！出埋啲厄錢狗","createTime":"2019-02-21T15:30:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-21T17:00:08.000Z","uid":124545,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"20e685e4f811db5491751160bcea7ce58895fc14","tid":1031412,"uid":124545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T15:30:27.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我同事有日就好唔開心 我就關心下佢到底咩事<br />\n原來佢傻妹屋企人有事 急要5萬<br />\n但佢fresh Grad邊有咁多 就問朋友借<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n朋友話得幾千人民幣 叫佢自己念辦法變港紙<br />\n佢就傻豬豬上網見到有個找換店 就過咗數比人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結果呢條浸大之恥就當然無過翻相應既錢比我朋友<br />\n我知佢on99 上網都好信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講真如果我即時知我都會屌到佢上天花板<br />\n我見佢最近喺公司日喊夜喊先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢真係好慘 fresh grad人工又唔係高 一厄比人厄5000<br />\n大家可以屌佢蠢 但幫幫手睇下可以點處理<br />\n已報警 但好明顯無用 警犬叫我同事結案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下係浸大厄錢狗既資料<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uztaArj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuztaArj.jpg&h=e3c9bb9f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n啱啱上網睇 佢已厄咗好多人"},{"pid":"cf63668b9ee8de4722be6d930a1a56fe987cda8d","tid":1031412,"uid":136186,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T15:33:01.000Z","msg":"塵大"},{"pid":"5a5477b6e1a8464432a0c7064e938ccb4c8f1dfa","tid":1031412,"uid":124545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf63668b9ee8de4722be6d930a1a56fe987cda8d","tid":1031412,"uid":136186,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T15:33:01.000Z","msg":"塵大"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T15:33:50.000Z","msg":"頂 唔記得佢地變咗塵大"},{"pid":"39d9dd9ab2a67a60bec3dea1e0d95ce3120bb92b","tid":1031412,"uid":123456,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T15:34:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咪撚結案<br />\nclose左警犬就唔洗做<br />\n冇clos